      <answers />
      <UID>3433</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>The man exchanges glances with the others. “Sure, why not?” he says with a shrug. “I’ll go with you. We wouldn’t want the boys getting any ideas now, would we?”</npc_text>
